1. *Smešna* priča nas je sve nasmejala. (The funny story made us all laugh.)
2. Ona je jako *smešna*, uvek me nasmeje. (She is very funny, she always makes me laugh.)
3. Tvoje šale su tako *smešne*, ne mogu da prestanem da se smejem. (Your jokes are so funny, I can't stop laughing.)
4. Moramo pronaći nešto *smešno* za proslavu rođendana. (We need to find something funny for the birthday celebration.)
5. Ova slika je baš *smešna*, pogledaj ovog psa. (This picture is really funny, look at this dog.)
6. Njegov pokušaj da bude *smešan* nije uspeo. (His attempt to be funny was unsuccessful.)
7. On je *smešan* lik, uvek radi neke čudne stvari. (He's a funny character, always doing some weird things.)
8. Smatram da je taj vic previše *smešan* za moju babu. (I think that joke is too funny for my grandma.)
9. Ta situacija je bila toliko *smešna* da nisam mogao da se suzdržim. (That situation was so funny that I couldn't help myself.)
10. Mnogi ljudi smatraju da je toalet papir *smešna* stvar za poklon, ali meni je potreban. (Many people think that toilet paper is a funny gift, but I need it.)